<h2 id=3D"important-check-before-pushing-publicly">Important check before p=
ushing publicly</h2>
<p>Before pushing to your personal/public GitHub, review these folders for =
sensitive info:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>connections/</code></li>
<li><code>profiles/</code></li>
<li><code>vaults/</code></li>
<li><code>data/</code></li>
</ul>
<p>Make sure you do <strong>not</strong> publish:</p>
<ul>
<li>passwords</li>
<li>tokens</li>
<li>secrets</li>
<li>private endpoints</li>
<li>customer/private data</li>
</ul>
<p>Good practice:</p>
<ul>
<li>keep configs parameterized</li>
<li>remove secret values</li>
<li>use sample/mock data only</li>
</ul>
