<ul>
<li><code>connections/</code></li>
<li><code>profiles/</code></li>
<li><code>vaults/</code></li>
<li><code>data/</code></li>
<li>any <code>.yaml</code>, <code>.py</code>, <code>.sql</code> with secret=
s or internal URLs</li>
</ul>
<p>Do <strong>not</strong> expose:</p>
<ul>
<li>passwords</li>
<li>API keys</li>
<li>tokens</li>
<li>client secrets</li>
<li>private endpoints</li>
<li>customer data</li>
<li>internal emails if sensitive</li>
</ul>
