<p>Review these folders before push:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>connections/</code></li>
<li><code>profiles/</code></li>
<li><code>vaults/</code></li>
<li><code>data/</code></li>
</ul>
<p>Make sure they do not contain:</p>
<ul>
<li>passwords</li>
<li>secrets</li>
<li>tokens</li>
<li>private URLs</li>
<li>customer data</li>
</ul>
<p>If they do, remove or sanitize them first.</p>
