Step 3: In Ascend, open each important file and copy its contents</h3>
<p>Start with the most important files:</p>
<h4 id=3D"root-files">Root files</h4>
<ul>
<li><code>README.md</code></li>
<li><code>ascend_project.yaml</code></li>
<li><code>.gitignore</code></li>
<li><code>.ascendignore</code></li>
</ul>
<h4 id=3D"main-folders">Main folders</h4>
<ul>
<li><code>flows/...</code></li>
<li><code>connections/...</code></li>
<li><code>automations/...</code></li>
<li><code>src/...</code></li>
<li><code>macros/...</code></li>
<li><code>profiles/...</code></li>
</ul>
<p>You do <strong>not</strong> need everything at once. Start with the core=
 project files.</p>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"step-4-paste-them-into-local-files">Step 4: Paste them into local=
 files</h3>
<p>Use VS Code, Notepad++, or any editor.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<ul>
<li>copy <code>ascend_project.yaml</code> from Ascend</li>
<li>create local <code>ascend_project.yaml</code></li>
<li>paste content</li>
<li>save</li>
</ul>
<p>Do the same for each file.</p>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"what-to-prioritize-first">What to prioritize first</h2>
<p>If your goal is to preserve your pipeline work, copy these first:</p>
<h3 id=3D"highest-priority">Highest priority</h3>
<ul>
<li><code>ascend_project.yaml</code></li>
<li><code>README.md</code></li>
<li>all files under <code>flows/</code></li>
<li>all files under <code>src/</code></li>
<li><code>macros/</code></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"next-priority">Next priority</h3>
<ul>
<li><code>automations/</code></li>
<li><code>connections/</code> (only if safe)</li>
<li><code>profiles/</code> (only if safe)</li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"be-careful-maybe-exclude-from-public-repo">Be careful / maybe exc=
lude from public repo</h3>
<ul>
<li><code>vaults/</code></li>
<li><code>data/</code> if it contains real data</li>
<li><code>connections/</code> if secrets/private endpoints appear</li>
<li><code>profiles/</code> if they contain sensitive settings</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id=3D"safer-public-repo-recommendation">Safer public repo recommendatio=
n</h1>
<p>Because your GitHub repo is public, I suggest:</p>
<h2 id=3D"include">Include</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>flows/</code></li>
<li><code>src/</code></li>
<li><code>macros/</code></li>
<li><code>automations/</code></li>
<li><code>README.md</code></li>
<li><code>ascend_project.yaml</code></li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"review-carefully-before-including">Review carefully before includ=
ing</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>connections/</code></li>
<li><code>profiles/</code></li>
<li><code>data/</code></li>
</ul>
<h2 id=3D"exclude-unless-sanitized">Exclude unless sanitized</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>vaults/</code></li>
</ul>
<hr>
