ery Ascend file</h1>
<p>For each file:</p>
<ol>
<li>open file in Ascend</li>
<li><strong>Ctrl + A</strong></li>
<li><strong>Ctrl + C</strong></li>
<li>open Notepad / VS Code</li>
<li>paste</li>
<li><strong>Save As</strong> with the same filename</li>
</ol>
