 companies in Sangamon County, Illinois. The flow ingests live hourly weath=
er history and forecast data, predicts high-wind risk for the next 3 days, =
joins those predictions to opted-in subscribers, produces alert-ready rows,=
 supports retrospective wind reporting, and will power a dashboard.

