ations from the Open-Meteo archive API.
- #component:read_</span>weather<span class=3D"hljs-emphasis">_forecast_</s=
pan>3d =E2=80=94 pulls the next 3 days of hourly forecast weather for the s=
ame locations from the Open-Meteo forecast API.
<span class=3D"hljs-bullet">-</span> #component:read<span class=3D"hljs-emp=
hasis">_weather_</span>history<span class=3D"hljs-emphasis">_3y_</span>marc=
h<span class=3D"hljs-emphasis">_nov =E2=80=94 pulls March-November hourly w=
eather history for the last 3 years for the same locations.

