phasis">_high_</span>wind<span class=3D"hljs-emphasis">_risk_</span>model =
=E2=80=94 trains a simple interpretable wind-risk scorer.
<span class=3D"hljs-bullet">-</span> #component:score<span class=3D"hljs-em=
